      <h1 class="post-title">Putin, a Guerra e o Fim da Lenda do Homem Invencível</h1>
      <p class="meta">Publicado em 2026-05-08 20:37:47</p>
      <figure class="post-thumb"><img src="https://fasgoncalves.github.io/fragmentoscaos-img/imagens/2b649666-57e6-4728-bfda-b92da5f83075.jpg" alt=""></figure>
      <div class="post-content">
        <div style="background:#0b0b0b; color:#e8eef4; font-family:Georgia,serif; line-height:2.2; padding:10px; text-align:left;">

<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" style="display:none;">
  <meta itemprop="headline" content="Putin, a Guerra e o Fim da Lenda do Homem Invencível">
