    <li><a href="https://www.factcheck.org/2022/03/the-facts-on-de-nazifying-ukraine/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#ffcc66;">FactCheck.org — The Facts on "De-Nazifying" Ukraine</a></li>
